## ðŸ—ï¸ 1ï¸âƒ£ IaaS vs PaaS vs SaaS (SOC VIEW, NOT MARKETING)

### ðŸ”¹ WHAT THEY MEAN

| Model | What Customer Manages | What Provider Manages | SOC Impact                      |
| ----- | --------------------- | --------------------- | ------------------------------- |
| IaaS  | OS, apps, identity    | Hardware, hypervisor  | Similar to onâ€‘prem + cloud logs |
