## ðŸ“œ 4ï¸âƒ£ CLOUD LOGGING BASICS (NONâ€‘NEGOTIABLE)

### ðŸ”¹ WHAT LOGS MATTER MOST

**Identity logs (Top Priority)**

* Signâ€‘ins
* MFA results
* Token issuance

**Audit logs**

* Role changes
